				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Oh man talk about what make me piss! I was in HoH oneday doing Kitting as usual with Druid Mage Necro and Wiz. Druid using DC pet to do the Kitting. Nothing is wrong until Wiz decide to go, while we waiting for replacement, Druid decide he want to test out his DC pet againt our (Mage and Necro) I picked necro first.... (65 necro mind you) the result is he won Necro pet with 60 pct heal!!! that not all the worst part is yet to come.... the druid said he havn't even put in Druid personal pet haste and DS yet OMG.... then the next target is me 62 mage... During the Kiting I was using Water pet and it has some of the druid buff such as skin, STR buff and PoT9 so I decide to give it a try. I did put up my DS on it and since druid see me put DS on he also put druid DS on the DC pet, however he still haven't use the haste... The result? DC pet kick water pet Ass with a little more than 50 PCT left OMG...
<br />

<br />
So I decide to give my 61 Air pet a try since I though it have stun might just make some different here. So I put up all the summon gear I can give. All the focus item on me. Belt, Haste mask, armor, Fist and Sword. Burnout V as well as DS. So it AC boost up a lot. this time druid decide to use his haste and see... The result? 
<br />

<br />
DC PET STILL KICK OUR ASS BY 48 PCT!!!! and DC pet is lv 45 mind you!!!!
