Magicians are good at:
<br />

<br />
- Summoned Focus items and pet toys
<br />
- Best ds in the game
<br />
- Best summoned pets in the game
<br />
- Nice nukes
<br />
- Depending on circumstances, extremely independent of needing boosted mana regen
<br />
- Depending on AA's, we can sustain tanking pets indefinitely, without any need to med, without needing clarity buffs or equipment, without needing slow or snare.
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">It all correct but one point DC can't be break! so it OFFICIALLY a PET not just charm pet anymore once AA ability landed</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
