that would suck, the only mobs that would be DCable that I can think of are the lesser elementals in BoT.........now I've had the awesome chance of having an enchanter die and/or gate when he had one of these DC'd, the specific encounter that I'm thinking about had SoV, muzzle, and blade for buffs/gifts and my 61 air pet with BO5, blades, and muzzle (no ds or girdle..........I'm lazy =b) took it down no problem with a good majority(60%+) of its hps left.  All in all I'd pass up the chance for a summoned only DC and take a summoned only snare
